---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Compleo Advisors · Rare Disease Strategy and Creative" description={"Rare disease strategy and creative firm. We work with rare disease biotechs, advocacy organizations, and pharma marketing services companies at moments of inflection."} slug="home" pathname="/" active="home">

<!-- ───────────────────────────  HEADER  ─────────────────────────── -->
<!-- ───────────────────────────  HERO  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner reveal">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Strategy · Positioning · Activation</div>
      <h1>Turning rare disease promise into <span class="accent">progress</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Strategy, positioning, and market movement.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-secondary">See how we work <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  POSITIONING  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="positioning reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <p>
      Compleo Advisors is a rare disease strategy and creative firm. We work with rare disease biotechs,
      advocacy organizations, and pharma marketing services companies at moments of inflection: when the
      market has shifted, an asset has advanced, or the business has outgrown its current strategy.
      What you get is a partner who knows this field from the inside: sharper direction, positioning that
      differentiates, and the market movement to drive progress.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  THREE PATHS  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="three-paths">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">Who we work with</p>
      <h2>Built for three audiences.</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">
        Each engagement begins with a diagnostic. Where you go from there depends on where you are.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="audience-cards">
      <article class="audience-card reveal">
        <div class="card-label">Rare Disease Biotechs</div>
        <h3>Are you a rare disease biotech at a commercial inflection point?</h3>
        <p>
          Your science is ready to move. What you need now is sharper positioning, a market narrative
          that earns credibility with the stakeholders who matter, and advocacy relationships that are
          intentional from the start.
        </p>
        <a href="/for-biotech" class="arrow-link">Explore biotech services</a>
      </article>

      <article class="audience-card reveal">
        <div class="card-label">Advocacy Organizations</div>
        <h3>Are you a rare disease advocacy organization ready to deepen your impact?</h3>
        <p>
          You hold urgency, trust, and deep community knowledge. Compleo Advisors helps translate that
          into structured strategy, compelling communication, and the industry partnerships that drive
          real progress for patients and families.
        </p>
        <a href="/for-advocacy" class="arrow-link">Explore advocacy services</a>
      </article>

      <article class="audience-card reveal">
        <div class="card-label">Pharma Marketing Services</div>
        <h3>Are you a pharma marketing services company looking to sharpen your market position?</h3>
        <p>
          You help pharmaceutical clients move markets and grow brands. Compleo Advisors works with marketing services
          organizations to define positioning, clarify go-to-market strategy, and build the market
          presence that draws the right clients and drives growth.
        </p>
        <a href="/for-pharma-marketing-services" class="arrow-link">Explore marketing services</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  FRAME · SOLVE · ACTIVATE  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="fsa">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fsa-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">A diagnostic-first approach</p>
      <h2>Frame. Solve. Activate.</h2>
      <p>
        Every engagement begins with diagnostic work. Compleo Advisors studies the business, the brand,
        and the market: what drives them, what holds them back, and where the real opportunity sits.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="fsa-grid">
      <div class="fsa-col reveal">
        <div class="step">Step 01</div>
        <h3>Frame.</h3>
        <p>Stakeholder insight, market research, and competitive analysis: the clarity that grounds every decision that follows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fsa-col reveal">
        <div class="step">Step 02</div>
        <h3>Solve.</h3>
        <p>Strategy, positioning, and narrative that moves audiences and grows markets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="fsa-col reveal">
        <div class="step">Step 03</div>
        <h3>Activate.</h3>
        <p>Execution that moves the market. Creative, campaigns, partnerships, and the work between.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fsa-footer reveal">
      <a href="/about" class="arrow-link">Read the full methodology</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  WHY COMPLEO ADVISORS  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="why">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="text-align:center;">What sets us apart</p>
      <h2>What makes Compleo Advisors different.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="why-list">
      <div class="why-item reveal">
        <h3>Rare disease is our focus.</h3>
        <p>
          This is the field we know intimately. Our work is shaped by the dynamics that define the rare
          disease ecosystem: profound urgency, high scientific complexity, strong collaboration with advocacy,
          and the high stakes of getting it right the first time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-item reveal">
        <h3>Senior leadership from start to finish.</h3>
        <p>
          Clients work directly with senior, strategic experts across every engagement. The thinking is
          not delegated. The work moves faster, the judgment is sharper, and the relationship stays close.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-item reveal">
        <h3>Strategy that becomes movement.</h3>
        <p>
          Compleo Advisors delivers strategy that becomes creative execution, market presence, and the
          partnerships that drive progress. The work moves from idea to activation without losing intent
          along the way.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  FOUNDER INTRO  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="founder">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="founder-grid">
      <div class="headshot-frame reveal" aria-label="Headshot placeholder">
        <div class="headshot-placeholder">
          <svg class="ph-mark" viewBox="0 0 180 180" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M 130.65,84.65 A 41,41 0 1 1 95.35,49.35" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A4A" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="118.99" cy="61.01" r="9" fill="#ED9105"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="ph-title">Headshot · Image 5</div>
          <div class="ph-sub">White blouse, light background.<br>Drop into <code style="background:#F5F5F5;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:3px;">/images/kristin.jpg</code></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="founder-copy reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Led by</p>
        <h2>Kristin Marvin Keller, Principal.</h2>
        <p>
          Kristin built Compleo Advisors to close a critical gap in rare disease: early-stage companies
          and advocacy organizations doing meaningful work without the strategic and creative support
          their communities deserve.
          She brings 25+ years of pharmaceutical and specific rare disease marketing experience, with
          20 years leading B2B strategy and commercial execution.
        </p>
        <a href="/about" class="arrow-link">Read her full background</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  CLOSING CTA  ─────────────────────────── -->
<section class="closing reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>If you are at a moment of inflection, we would welcome a conversation.</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start a conversation <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
    <span class="alt-email">
      Or write directly to <a href="mailto:kristin@compleoadvisors.com">kristin@compleoadvisors.com</a>
    </span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ───────────────────────────  FOOTER  ─────────────────────────── -->

</SiteLayout>

<style is:global>
/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   COMPLEO ADVISORS — HOMEPAGE MOCKUP v1
   Phase 1 of website redesign · Single-file HTML
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */

/* Tokens — pulled from Compleo Advisors Brand Standard v3 */
/* tokens in global.css */

/* Reset / base */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  font-size: var(--fs-body);
  line-height: var(--lh-body);
  color: var(--c-body);
  background: var(--c-white);
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
}
img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
a { color: var(--c-charcoal); text-decoration: none; transition: color .15s ease; }
a:hover { color: var(--c-amber); }

h1, h2, h3, h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: var(--lh-tight);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
h1 { font-size: var(--fs-h1-desktop); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
h2 { font-size: var(--fs-h2-desktop); font-weight: 600; }
h3 { font-size: var(--fs-h3-desktop); font-weight: 500; line-height: var(--lh-snug); }

p { margin: 0 0 1em; }
p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

/* Container */
.container {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: var(--content-max);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}
.container-narrow {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: var(--content-narrow);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--gutter);
}

/* Sections */
section {
  padding: var(--section-y-desktop) 0;
}
section.tight { padding: calc(var(--section-y-desktop) * 0.6) 0; }
.section-band-cream { background: var(--c-warm-cream); }
.section-band-gray  { background: var(--c-light-gray); }

/* Eyebrow / small label */
.eyebrow {
  font-size: var(--fs-small);
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  margin: 0 0 16px;
}

/* Buttons */
.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 14px 26px;
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background .18s ease, color .18s ease, border-color .18s ease, transform .18s ease;
}
.btn-primary {
  background: var(--c-amber);
  color: var(--c-white);
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background: var(--c-charcoal);
  color: var(--c-white);
}
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--c-rule-gray);
}
.btn-secondary:hover {
  border-color: var(--c-charcoal);
  color: var(--c-near-black);
}
.btn .arrow { display: inline-block; transition: transform .18s ease; }
.btn:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

/* Inline arrow link */
.arrow-link {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.arrow-link::after {
  content: "→";
  transition: transform .18s ease;
}
.arrow-link:hover { color: var(--c-amber); }
.arrow-link:hover::after { transform: translateX(4px); }

/* Amber rule (thin section divider) */
.amber-rule {
  display: block;
  width: 48px;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--c-amber);
  border: 0;
  margin: 0 0 28px;
}
.amber-rule.center { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   HEADER / NAV
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.site-header {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
  backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: saturate(180%) blur(10px);
  border-bottom: var(--rule);
}
.nav {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 18px 0;
}
.brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 12px;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
}
.brand-mark {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
}
.brand-words {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  line-height: 1;
}
.brand-name {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 18px;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  letter-spacing: -0.005em;
}
.brand-sub {
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  margin-top: 4px;
}
.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 28px;
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
}
.nav-links a {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.nav-cta {
  margin-left: 10px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background: var(--c-amber);
  color: var(--c-white) !important;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--c-charcoal); color: var(--c-white) !important; }

.nav-toggle {
  display: none;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  font-size: 22px;
  padding: 8px;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   HERO — wide editorial, no image
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  padding: 84px 0 72px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-inner {
  max-width: 1080px;
}
.hero-eyebrow {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  margin-bottom: 44px;
}
.hero-eyebrow::before {
  content: "";
  display: inline-block;
  width: 48px;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--c-amber);
}
.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(44px, 7.2vw, 88px);
  line-height: 1.04;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  max-width: 18ch;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
}
.hero h1 .accent {
  color: var(--c-amber);
  background-image: linear-gradient(var(--c-amber), var(--c-amber));
  background-size: 100% 6px;
  background-position: 0 96%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  padding-bottom: 2px;
}
.hero-sub {
  font-size: clamp(20px, 2.1vw, 24px);
  line-height: 1.45;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  max-width: 56ch;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
  font-weight: 400;
}
.hero-ctas {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 14px;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   POSITIONING CALLOUT
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.positioning {
  background: var(--c-warm-cream);
  padding: var(--section-y-desktop) 0;
  position: relative;
}
.positioning::before,
.positioning::after {
  content: "";
  display: block;
  width: 48px;
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--c-amber);
  margin: 0 auto 32px;
}
.positioning::after { margin: 32px auto 0; }
.positioning p {
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  text-align: center;
  max-width: 880px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   THREE PATHS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.three-paths h2 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.three-paths .section-intro {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  font-size: 17px;
  margin: 0 auto 32px;
  max-width: 600px;
}
.audience-cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 28px;
}
.audience-card {
  background: var(--c-white);
  border: var(--rule);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 40px 36px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  transition: border-color .2s ease, transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
}
.audience-card:hover {
  border-color: var(--c-amber);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 14px 32px -16px rgba(74, 74, 74, 0.18);
}
.audience-card .card-label {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.audience-card h3 {
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 1.3;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}
.audience-card p {
  color: var(--c-body);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  flex-grow: 1;
  margin-bottom: 26px;
}
.audience-card .arrow-link { font-size: 15px; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   FRAME. SOLVE. ACTIVATE.
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.fsa {
  background: var(--c-light-gray);
}
.fsa-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
}
.fsa-header .eyebrow { text-align: center; }
.fsa-header h2 { margin-bottom: 24px; }
.fsa-header p {
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  max-width: 680px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  font-size: 18px;
}
.fsa-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 48px;
}
.fsa-col {
  text-align: left;
}
.fsa-col .step {
  font-family: var(--font-stack);
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.fsa-col h3 {
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.fsa-col p {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.fsa-footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 32px;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   WHY COMPLEO ADVISORS
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.why {
  padding-top: var(--section-y-desktop);
  padding-bottom: var(--section-y-desktop);
}
.why-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
}
.why-header h2 { margin-bottom: 0; }
.why-list {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 28px;
}
.why-item {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
  align-items: start;
}
.why-item h3 {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  line-height: 1.25;
  padding-top: 4px;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--c-amber);
  padding-left: 20px;
}
.why-item p {
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   FOUNDER INTRO
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.founder {
  background: var(--c-warm-cream);
}
.founder-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 360px 1fr;
  gap: 72px;
  align-items: center;
}
.headshot-frame {
  position: relative;
  aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
  background: var(--c-white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  border: 1px solid var(--c-rule-gray);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 18px 36px -22px rgba(74, 74, 74, 0.25);
}
.headshot-placeholder {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 24px;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
}
.headshot-placeholder .ph-mark {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  margin: 0 auto 16px;
  opacity: 0.4;
}
.headshot-placeholder .ph-title {
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 14px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.headshot-placeholder .ph-sub {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--c-mid-gray);
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.founder-copy .eyebrow { margin-bottom: 14px; }
.founder-copy h2 {
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
}
.founder-copy p {
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   CLOSING CTA
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.closing {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--c-warm-cream) 0%, #FBE7C8 100%);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 60px 0;
}
.closing h2 {
  font-size: clamp(28px, 3.4vw, 40px);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--c-near-black);
  margin: 0 auto 24px;
  max-width: 22ch;
  line-height: 1.25;
}
.closing .btn { margin: 0 auto; }
.closing .alt-email {
  display: block;
  margin-top: 24px;
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--c-charcoal);
}
.closing .alt-email a { color: var(--c-amber); font-weight: 500; }

/* ─────────────────────────────────────────────
   FOOTER
   ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.site-footer {
  background: var(--c-near-black);
  color: #B3B3B3;
  padding: 64px 0 32px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.footer-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}
.footer-brand .brand-name { color: var(--c-white); }
.footer-brand .brand-sub { color: #888; }
.footer-tag {
  margin-top: 16px;
  color: #B3B3B3;
  max-width: 32ch;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.footer-col h4 {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--c-amber);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.footer-col ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
.footer-col li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
.footer-col a { color: #B3B3B3; }
.footer-col a:hover { color: var(--c-white); }
.footer-bottom {
  border-top: 1px solid #444;
  padding-top: 24px;
  display: flex;
